remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-118">默认值为`value`参数使用空字符串 ("")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-118">The default for the `value` parameter uses the empty string ("").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-119">`value`参数<xref:System.Net.Cookie>不能`null`引用 (在 Visual Basic 中为 Nothing)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-119">The `value` parameter for a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> must not be a `null` reference (Nothing in Visual Basic).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="15f58-120">以分号 （";"） 和逗号 （"，"） 字符是保留字符，不能在传递`value`参数中传递的字符串，除非`value`参数括在双引号内。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-120">The semicolon (";") and comma (",") characters are reserved and cannot be passed in the `value` parameter unless the string passed in the `value` parameter is enclosed in double quotes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="15f58-121">因此下面的示例构造函数会成功，但当您尝试添加此<xref:System.Net.Cookie>到<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>实例与<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)>或<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)>方法，该操作将失败并引发异常：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-121">So the following example constructor would succeed, but when you try to add this <xref:System.Net.Cookie> to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance with the <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)> or <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)> methods, the operation will fail and throw an exception:</span></span>  
  
 ```csharp
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "123,456");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-122">但是，将创建以下构造函数有了这些特殊字符转义<xref:System.Net.Cookie>，可以将其添加到<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>实例：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-122">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  
 
 ```csharp
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "\"123,456\"");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```
  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-123">逗号字符用作分隔符之间的同一行上单独的 cookie。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-123">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-141">默认值为`path`参数使用空字符串 ("")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-141">The default for the `path` parameter uses the empty string ("").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-142">`value`参数<xref:System.Net.Cookie>不能`null`引用 (在 Visual Basic 中为 Nothing)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-142">The `value` parameter for a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> must not be a `null` reference (Nothing in Visual Basic).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="15f58-143">以分号 （";"） 和逗号 （"，"） 字符是保留字符，不能在传递`value`参数中传递的字符串，除非`value`参数括在双引号内。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-143">The semicolon (";") and comma (",") characters are reserved and cannot be passed in the `value` parameter unless the string passed in the `value` parameter is enclosed in double quotes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="15f58-144">因此下面的示例构造函数会成功，但当您尝试添加此<xref:System.Net.Cookie>到<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>实例与<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)>或<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)>方法，该操作将失败并引发异常：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-144">So the following example constructor would succeed, but when you try to add this <xref:System.Net.Cookie> to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance with the <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Net.Cookie)> or <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer.Add(System.Uri,System.Net.Cookie)> methods, the operation will fail and throw an exception:</span></span>  
  
 ```csharp
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "123,456", "");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-145">但是，将创建以下构造函数有了这些特殊字符转义<xref:System.Net.Cookie>，可以将其添加到<xref:System.Net.CookieContainer>实例：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-145">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  
 
 ```csharp
 System.Net.Cookie cookie = new System.Net.Cookie("contoso", "\"123,456\"", "");
 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ``` 
  
 <span data-ttu-id="15f58-146">逗号字符用作分隔符之间的同一行上单独的 cookie。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15f58-146">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>

  
  
